data.description: Located in popular Brindlewood subdivision and the Hamilton Local school district, this charming 3 bedroom, one bath ranch has open concept living with a spacious kitchen directly off the great room with vaulted ceiling. 1 car attached garage, updated bathroom, fenced in backyard with deck and storage shed, covered front porch, Roof was replaced in 2012. Freshly painted and ready to move in.
